seo: 通达OA,漏洞检测,文件上传,后台getshell
seo_en: Tongda OA, vulnerability detection, file upload, backdoor getshell
summary: 该插件用于检测通达OA V11.2版本的后台文件上传漏洞，并尝试利用该漏洞获取WebShell。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the backend file upload vulnerability of Tongda OA V11.2 and attempt to exploit this vulnerability to obtain a WebShell.
